{"tid":2142923,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"丟煙被刑事檢控　律師批評弄權","createTime":"2020-08-06T18:36:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-06T19:33:46.000Z","uid":240362,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"773940116cb20ba406b826a87e29db777b581445","tid":2142923,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T18:36:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200807/SKVFDSLJ3MT5FRWWWMH4Q3Q4NU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200807%2FSKVFDSLJ3MT5FRWWWMH4Q3Q4NU%2F&d=il%2BrReVPph3FBkDtfLAFOkB1UtkZy1G9%2FYekDAkGV2Y%3D&h=720ae1af\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200807%2FSKVFDSLJ3MT5FRWWWMH4Q3Q4NU%2F&h=44693ead\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200807/SKVFDSLJ3MT5FRWWWMH4Q3Q4NU/</a><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】去年12月1日「毋忘初心」反修例遊行，隊頭抵紅磡後爆警民衝突。其間一名男子被指在警員前丟煙頭，並曾拒出示身份證。男子昨承認在公眾地方亂拋廢料罪，主任裁判官嚴舜儀判罰款1,500元。亂拋垃圾一般以定額罰款處理，但本案動用刑事控罪，定罪最高判監三個月。有律師質疑警方選擇控罪用意，用程序欺壓市民。"},{"pid":"dd9caa6949f68ab3df149497dc27849bb80aeaa0","tid":2142923,"uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T18:36:46.000Z","msg":"律師陳惠源指警方用程序欺壓市民，無法體現公義，「掟咗一萬個煙頭，點解第一萬零一個變咗『廢料』？咁代表啲咩呢？如果（檢控）唔係為咗尋找公義，唯一嘅解釋就係弄權。」"},{"pid":"9c5b77c6f4610c5ec063a3d73a5940336e5af2d8","tid":2142923,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T18:45:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a719a6ae15df805bb8a43cc3f06c74951de4bf36","tid":2142923,"uid":20867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T18:48:37.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">Miss YIM Shun-yee, Ada</code></pre><br